# Implement Instapaper-like Themes

The goal is to replicate the reading experience of Instapaper by implementing its four core color themes and adjusting the layout for a focus on readability.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Using user-provided hex codes for all themes.
> Prioritizing update of [src/pages/list00.astro](file:///d:/yonggeun/porter/git/o-m.kr/src/pages/list00.astro).

## Proposed Changes

### Styles
#### [MODIFY] [theme.css](file:///d:/yonggeun/porter/git/o-m.kr/src/styles/theme.css)
- Define the four Instapaper themes using CSS variables:
  - **Paper**: Bg `#ffffff`, Text `#000000`
  - **Coffee**: Bg `#f8f2e4`, Text `#242424`
  - **Gray**: Bg `#3c3c3c`, Text `#d2d2d2`
  - **Midnight**: Bg `#111111`, Text `#ffffff`

#### [MODIFY] [global.css](file:///d:/yonggeun/porter/git/o-m.kr/src/styles/global.css)
- Apply the **Coffee** theme variables to the `:root` or `body` by default.
- Adjust typography:
  - Font: Serif for body.
  - Line-height: 1.6.
  - Max-width: 700px.

### Pages
#### [MODIFY] [list00.astro](file:///d:/yonggeun/porter/git/o-m.kr/src/pages/list00.astro)
- Update to use the new theme variables and layout styles.

